('From Nerds to Beauties', 3337, 'Two unusual girlfriends - Little Mermaid and Arlene - embark on an exciting journey into the world of stylish transformation. Their appearance, full of flaws, requires magical intervention. In the first stage of the game, the girls go through a series of fun cosmetic procedures: from cleansing masks to magical elixirs that give them radiant skin and luxurious hair. With each successful step, they become more attractive. In the second stage, the player will have to become a real stylist for girls, choosing unique hairstyles, fashionable clothes and bright accessories for the heroines that will emphasize the individuality of the girlfriends. In this game, friendship, self-expression and fun go hand in hand, and each small victory brings the Little Mermaid and Arlene closer to their dream of becoming real beauties!', 'Help two girl friends to transform their appearance and choose a hairstyle clothes and accessories Depending on the gaming device either a click of a computer mouse or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it', 'English'),
('Level Devil 3D', 3338, 'Level Devil 3D is a fast-paced game that constantly tests your ability to react to the unexpected. Navigate through sudden obstacles and hidden pitfalls as you race toward the emergency exit. In this ever-surprising world, each step brings new twists, fueling curiosity about the challenges ahead. Stay mentally prepared&amp;mdash;dangers can appear at any moment. Maintaining focus and composure is key to overcoming the toughest hurdles. Your objective is simple: overcome obstacles and reach the door at the end of the path to progress to the next level. But with every stage comes a fresh challenge, offering players a dynamic perspective on the difficu', 'To move Use the arrow keys or WASD keys To jump Use the spacebar', 'English'),
('CluckNRun', 3339, 'Embark on a thrilling journey through the countryside in ClucknRun, where your mission is to return a lost chickens to their farm home! Navigate through vibrant farm landscapes, collecting bountiful chickens and essential gasoline along the way. But be cautious&amp;mdash;barrels are scattered across the path, ready to derail your ride!', 'Use the A and D keys for smooth left and right movement or simply control the flow with your mouse for an effortless experience', 'English'),
('GT Burnout Parking Simulator', 3340, 'GT Burnout Parking Simulator is a thrilling driving game that challenges players to master precision parking while performing intense burnout maneuvers. Take control of powerful GT cars and navigate through intricate parking courses filled with tight corners, obstacles, and time-based challenges. Feel the adrenaline rush as you execute perfect drifts, burn rubber, and park with ultimate precision. With realistic physics, stunning visuals, and various difficulty levels, GT Burnout Parking Simulator offers an exciting mix of skill-based driving and stylish stunts. Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate parking master?', 'WASD arrow key - move', 'English'),
('Roll Classic', 3341, 'Roll Classic is a timeless dice game that combines strategy and luck. Players take turns rolling dice to collect points, aiming to reach a target score before their opponents. With each roll, players must decide whether to risk it all for more points or hold back to secure their lead. The game offers thrilling twists, where the unexpected can change the course of the game. Quick to learn, yet endlessly engaging, Roll Classic is perfect for family and friends.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Connect the Balls 2', 3342, 'In the second part of the new online game Connect the Balls 2 you will continue to play through an interesting puzzle. In front of you on the screen you will see a playing field on which there will be round dots of different colors. You will need to inspect everything carefully. Find two identical dots of the same color. Now connect them using the mouse with one line. Having done this, you will see how these points will disappear from the playing field. By making your moves, you will completely clear the field of dots and then move on to the next level of the game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Shoot Balls', 3343, 'Try to break as Colored bricks as possible and avoid to break as white bricks! Game Made with Construct 2. Touch &amp;amp; Mouse control! Thanks for play.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Unreal Descent 2: Race', 3344, 'Unreal Descent 2: Race is a sequel to the popular arcade game, in which players go on exciting and extreme descents. The new part of the game has improved graphics, added new levels and tracks, as well as unique vehicles to make the races even more spectacular and dynamic. Each descent is a chance to show your agility and ingenuity to come first to the finish line. The game Unreal Descent 2: Race offers players a unique opportunity to experience the adrenaline of high-speed descents. Get ready for a real survival race, where only speed and reaction can lead to victory!', 'Controls for PC Gas W up arrow Brake S down arrow Turn right D right arrow Turn left A left arrow Nitro C Change view F Controls for phones On-screen steering wheel On-screen buttons The mode is switched in the game settings', 'English'),
('Qolor 2048', 3345, 'Slide into the addictive chaos of 2048! Merge tiles, double up, and chase that elusive 2048 in a sleek 4x4 grid. Simple moves, big thrills', 'For Desktop Use Arrow Keys-Up Down Left Right For Mobile Swipe-Left Right Up Down', 'English'),
('Mighty Run 2D', 3346, 'Mighty Run is an exciting platformer where you jump, dodge obstacles, and battle enemies to reach the next level. Collect gifts along the way and grab the diamond at the end to unlock new challenges. Use power-ups, master tricky jumps, and overcome tough obstacles in this action-packed adventure. With smooth controls, vibrant graphics, and engaging gameplay, every level tests your skills and reflexes. Can you collect all the rewards and conquer every stage? Play', 'Controls for Mighty Run - Left Arrow ndash Move Left - Right Arrow ndash Move Right - Up Arrow ndash Jump', 'English');
