('Solo Quiz ing', 3353, 'Step into the shadowy world of Solo Leveling with this fast-paced anime quiz! Test your knowledge of Sung Jin-Woo&amp;rsquo;s journey, the mysterious leveling system, epic battles, and powerful shadow soldiers. Whether youre a casual fan or a hardcore hunter, these 10 questions will challenge your memory and immerse you in the dark fantasy universe of Solo Leveling.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Labubu World Game', 3354, 'Labubu World is a fun and quirky adventure game that brings the mischievous character Labubu to life in a colorful, whimsical world. Players step into a universe full of surprises, where every stage is packed with unique challenges, hidden treasures, and playful creatures. In this game, you guide Labubu through vibrant levels, jumping across platforms, solving puzzles, and avoiding tricky obstacles. Each world has its own theme and personality&amp;mdash;whether it&amp;rsquo;s enchanted forests, mysterious caves, or candy-colored skies. Collect items along the way to unlock new abilities and customize your Labubu with fun outfits.', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Card Quest: Solitaire', 3355, 'Embark on an epic journey through the world of cards in Card Quest: Solitaire! This is not just another solitaire &amp;ndash; it&amp;rsquo;s a true adventure where every move matters. Master the classic solitaire rules, explore multiple themes, and challenge yourself with unique scoring modes. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re here to relax or to chase the highest score, the quest never ends! With smooth controls, beautiful backgrounds, and unlimited replayability, Card Quest: Solitaire will keep you coming back for just one more game. Are you ready to begin your quest?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
