('Dino Rush', 3364, 'Get ready for an exciting adventure with our cute dino! Dino Rush is a fun and easy-to-play arcade game where you help a light-blue dinosaur run and jump over obstacles. The gameplay is simple but full of challenges, and the more you play, the faster and more thrilling it becomes! Perfect for all ages, featuring smooth cartoon graphics and a retro arcade vibe. Test your skills, aim for the highest score, and challenge your friends!', 'Jump Space or Touch', 'English'),
