('Space Surfer', 3366, 'Welcome to Space Surfer! Get ready for the ultimate hyperspace challenge! Space Surfer is a thrilling 3D arcade game that sends you blasting through a dazzling, high-speed tunnel of light and color. Your mission is simple: survive the cosmic chaos, dodge dangerous obstacles, and grab as many rewards as you can to become a legend of the vortex. Do you have the reflexes to master the tunnel? How to Play: Your Mission Briefing Survive the Rush!', 'Mouse click or tap to play Easy Controls Controlling your ship is incredibly intuitive Just click and drag your mouse or use your finger on a touchscreen to glide around the space tunnel Your ship will follow you instantly', 'English');
