('Combine food of the USSR', 3467, 'A game in an unusual setting! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone where food falls and connects if it is the same! Connect as much food as possible, accumulate points! Become the first on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to combine food but over time there will be more and more of it', 'English'),
('Nugget Collector', 3468, 'Nugget Collector is a fun and engaging puzzle game where players must skillfully collect nuggets that fall from above into a bucket. The game is set against a charming wooden backdrop that gives it a rustic and cozy feel. As nuggets fall, players must draw paths to guide them into the bucket while avoiding obstacles and ensuring none of the nuggets are lost.', 'Objective Your goal is to collect all the falling nuggets into the bucket by drawing paths Controls Simply swipe your finger to draw lines on the screen that will act as guides for the nuggets Avoid Obstacles Watch out for obstacles like rocks and wo', 'English'),
('Wood Block Puzzle 2', 3469, 'Wood Block Puzzle 2 is a captivating puzzle game that tasks players with arranging wooden blocks to fill complete rows and columns on a grid. With simple drag-and-drop mechanics, players strategically place blocks to create solid lines and clear the board. The game features various modes, including Classic and Challenge, each offering unique gameplay experiences. With its minimalist design and relaxing gameplay, Wood Block Puzzle 2 provides hours of entertainment for puzzle enthusiasts of all skill levels.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Dessert Stack Run', 3470, 'Enter a world of delicious desserts and exciting parkour challenges. In Dessert Stack Run, you&amp;rsquo;ll become the ultimate dessert master. Keep running across colorful platforms, collecting tasty food,and stacking them into the tallest and yummiest dessert tower!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Color Helix: Spin It', 3471, 'Dive into a dynamic world of color and speed! In this exciting arcade game, you control a ball that rolls along a rotating cylinder. There are obstacles painted in different colors along the way. Your task is to turn the cylinder so that the ball passes through sections of its color. But be careful! The ball can change its color right during the level, making the task more difficult. Each new stage offers increasingly complex combinations, testing your reaction and ability to make quick decisions. Game features: Exciting gameplay with intuitive controls. Colorful levels with a unique design. Gradually increasing difficulty.', 'Control the rotation of the cylinder so that the ball passes through obstacles of its color Turn the cylinder left or right avoiding sections of other colors The ball will roll automatically', 'English'),
('Find the Sprunki', 3472, 'Find out the hidden Sprunki in the specified images. Each level has 12 hidden Sprunki. There are 12 levels in total. The time is limited so be fast and find all hidden objects before time runs out. Clicking in the wrong place several times reduces the time by an additional 5 seconds. So, if you are ready, start the game and have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Finish the Drawing', 3473, 'Finish The Drawing is your invitation to complete drawings in each level! Showcase your skill by drawing the missing part of each image, revealing charming scenes and characters. Each stroke is a piece of the artistic puzzle, challenging your creativity. Master the art of detail and immerse yourself in a world of drawings awaiting your completion. Ready to bring the images to life with your pencils?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Car Repair And Wash', 3474, 'Car washing garage games are a fun and exciting way to enjoy the thrill of car cleaning and customizing virtual cars. In these car washing auto mechanic games, you step into the shoes of a car mechanic and get to work in an Auto garage filled with dirty, dusty, and sometimes even incredibly messy vehicles. Your mission is to transform these dirty cars into sparkling, shiny masterpieces. These mechanic simulator car games allow you to explore your creativity, choosing from various car cleaning tools, paints, and accessories to make the cars look their best.', 'Mouse click or tap to play Features of car washing mechanic simulator Experience the fun of washing repairing and customizing virtual cars just like a car mechanic Choose from various tools paints and accessories to make cars look unique and stylish', 'English'),
('Fierce Battle Breakout', 3475, 'This is a fast-paced 3D mini-game that combines survival, combat and strategy. Players will play the role of survivors striving for survival. Facing the threats from enemies, the pursuit of hostile forces and the harsh environment, they will embark on a thrilling journey of survival and defense. The difficulty of the levels will keep increasing. Each level has a large number of enemies constantly swarming towards the players. Players need to eliminate all the enemies to win. Meanwhile, powerful bosses will randomly appear in the levels, which adds to the challenge of the game. The operation of the game is relatively simple and easy to learn,', 'Control the movement of the character through means such as virtual joysticks or touching the screen For example manipulate the character to move nimbly and avoid the attacks of enemies You can also make use of the obstacles and terrain advantages in t', 'English'),
('CRAZY BALL PICKER', 3476, 'If you are ready, try to get the balls thrown upwards into the bucket by drawing lines. Dont let the balls fall down. Lets see how many balls you can collect, You only have the right to draw three lines.', 'Mobile Controls Hold your finger on the screen and drag to draw a line PC Controls Hold the left mouse button and drag to draw a line', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Pixcade Squid', 3477, 'In the world of the twin pixel brothers, there are chests they need to collect, and they must gather the chests to move on to the next level. Of course, collecting the chests wont be easy. While collecting the chests, there are coins they need to gather as well. They must collect all the coins and complete the level. Help the brothers and assist them in completing the level.', 'Press WASD and Arrow keys to move Find and collect the two chests and coins Be careful of the spikes on the map', 'English'),
('Bubble run', 3478, 'Move forward on the platform and destroy the pop it characters or dodge them. Be careful and react quickly to the approaching enemies.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Merge Flowers in 2D!', 3479, 'A game in an unusual setting! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone, where flowers fall and connect if they are the same! Connect as many flowers as possible to get the most beautiful one, collect points! Become the first on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to connect flowers but over time there will be more and more of them Once you connect the biggest flower in this game it will disappear and give you the most points', 'English'),
('Mega Makeup   Seasons Best', 3480, 'Mega Makeup Seasons Best is the ultimate makeup game where creativity knows no bounds! Design stunning looks for each month of the year with vibrant eyeshadows, bold lipsticks, sparkling gems, and stylish accessories. Choose between Pro Mode for precision or Freestyle Mode for endless color combinations. Complete your seasonal masterpiece with matching jewelry and hair accessories. Perfect for makeup enthusiasts, this game is your go-to for all things beauty and style! Play now!', 'Use your mouse to play the game on a desktop tap to play on mobile devices', 'English'),
('Fruit Slicer Classic', 3481, 'Enter the Fruit Slicer Classic, a relaxing and casual fruit-cutting game. You&amp;rsquo;ll use your weapon to slice through many fruits. Release the knife and cut through them. Pass the level with the fewest shots to get more rewards. Get coins to unlock more cool knives and increase your fruit-cutting damage.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Jiggle Master Man', 3482, 'Jiggle master is a best game for time consuming process, you can play like applying logical thinking on every level. In every new level you can feel like exciting.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Baby Ice Princess Phone', 3483, 'This is a mobile simulator game for girls and kids. Do you want to talk to the ice princess? Do you want to take care of cute unicorns? If you are interested in all this, our game is for you. This collection of educational mobile games contains many modes. Just press the colored buttons and you can talk to the snow princess.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Roguelike RPG', 3484, 'Roguelike RPG is an immersive adventure game where players explore ever-changing RPG maps filled with dangerous monsters. Strategize, fight, and destroy these creatures to survive, collect loot, and grow stronger with each run. Every decision matters in this thrilling roguelike journey! Use WASD to walk , E to get weapons or anything in map and mouse click left to attack', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Spra racing cars speed', 3485, 'Speed Racing Cars is a high-octane racing game where you can choose the best cars and unlock powerful supercars. Tune your vehicles in the customization menu, upgrade their performance, and expand your collection by purchasing new rides. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.kizi10.org/''&gt;https://www.kizi10.org/&lt;/a&gt; . Hit the track and race like a pro through stunning environments, pushing your limits to dominate the competition! Use wasd to drive and c to change camera', 'wasd to drive', 'English'),
('Monster Makeover Make Dance', 3486, 'Monster Makeover: Make &amp;amp; Dance - Create Your Own Unique Monsters! Unleash your imagination and dive into the world of Monster Makeover: Make &amp;amp; Dance, the ultimate game for monster lovers! Are you ready to embark on a thrilling adventure of monster creation and dance? Get ready to experience the most exciting and entertaining monster makeover game on the Puzzle games market!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('FruitSwipe', 3487, 'This game is a fun and challenging casual puzzle game designed specifically for players who love fruits and puzzle solving. In this colorful world of fruits, you will embark on a wonderful journey to find, connect, and eliminate delicious fruits. The game combines classic line elimination gameplay with modern visual effects, bringing you an unprecedented gaming experience. The game interface is filled with various fruits, such as bright strawberries, juicy oranges, sweet apples, etc It is an excellent choice for relaxing the mind and exercising the brain. No complex operations are required, but it can bring a sense of accomplishment and spend', 'By sliding your fingers connect fruits of the same type to form an uninterrupted path Once the number of fruits on the path reaches or exceeds the specified elimination limit 3 or more they will disappear brilliantly adding a touch of freshness to y', 'English'),
('Merge Pisces from the Ocean!', 3488, 'A game with an underwater atmosphere! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone where fish fall and connect if they have the same color! Connect as many fish as possible to get the biggest one, collect points! Become the first on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to connect the fish but over time there will be more and more of them', 'English'),
('Flappy Bird Spinning oia oia Cat', 3489, 'Get ready for the craziest and most distracting Flappy Bird experience ever! Flappy Bird Spinning Oia Oia Cat takes the classic flappy mechanics but cranks up the madness. This time, you&amp;rsquo;re not dodging pipes&amp;mdash;you&amp;rsquo;re navigating through giant log wood obstacles while the Oia Oia Cat spins faster and faster in the background with every jump! How to Play Just like the original Flappy Bird, tap the screen (or click the mouse) to make your bird flap its wings and stay airborne. Your goal is to dodge the massive log wood barriers that stand in your way. Precision and perfect timing are key&amp;mdash;one wrong move and it&amp;rsquo;s game over!', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('100 Doors Escape Mysteries', 3490, 'Go to unlock 100 mysterious doors. Try to solve complex puzzles. You need to use your intelligence and wisdom to escape from one room after another.Use your logic to find the key to escape. Come to try it.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Master jumping', 3491, 'Sit on the splits right between the two walls. You need to get to the very top, but the walls can be glass or with sharp spikes, where twine will not help.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Foot Doctor : Feet Care', 3492, 'ouch!!!! these feet are in poor conditions. It is now really urgent to cure them. As a doctor, you are going to take care of the feet of your patients. Use all your tools to cure them. It''s super easy and fun.', 'ouch these feet are in poor conditions It is now really urgent to cure them As a doctor you are going to take care of the feet of your patients Use all your tools to cure them It s super easy and fun', 'English'),
('BTS Sprunki Valentine Coloring', 3493, 'BTS Sprunki Valentine Coloring is a fun and free online coloring game designed for kids. With four unique images to color, you can unleash your creativity and create a masterpiece. Enjoy a relaxing and entertaining experience as you bring each picture to life with vibrant colors. Play now and have fun!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Animals Mix Up   AI Hybrid', 3494, 'Discover unique combinations of animals and everyday things in this exciting game! Just pick two animals, and the AI will use a special algorithm to blend them together.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Skibidi Toilet Squid Game Honeycomb', 3495, 'Skibidi Toilet Squid Game Honeycomb is a precision challenge game where players must carefully carve out specific shapes from a honeycomb without breaking it. Inspired by the Squid Game honeycomb challenge, players control Skibidi Toilet and must use steady hands and patience to trace intricate shapes within a time limit. Breaking the honeycomb results in failure, while successful completion unlocks new, more complex patterns. The game&amp;rsquo;s tense atmosphere, combined with high-pressure gameplay, keeps players on the edge of their seats!', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Cleaning Princess', 3496, 'This is an ASMR game for girls. If you like to clean everything, our game is right for you. The game has 5 modes: ear cleaning, heel cleaning, back spa, teeth cleaning, and fan cleaning. You can use different tools to clean and massage your body parts. But it is important to note that each mode has a countdown time and you must choose the right tool to do the cleaning.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('BusParking', 3497, 'This is a challenging and fun simulation parking game designed for players who love driving and pursue precise operations. In this highly realistic 3D gaming world, you will transform into a highly skilled driver, facing various complex and ever-changing parking scenes, each level testing your driving skills and spatial judgment ability. Exquisite 3D graphics and realistic sound effects make you feel as if you are in a real driving environment. While enjoying the fun of gaming, one can also learn practical parking techniques and enhance their awareness of driving safety in real life. The game includes over a hundred carefully designed levels,', 'Keyboard key c to switch lenses Keyboard key r switches forward backward Keyboard button w come on Keyboard key s brake Turn left on keyboard key a Turn right on keyboard key d Press the ESC key on the keyboard to pause the game', 'English'),
('Chill Math Multiplication', 3498, 'In this game, a winter image is hidden beneath multiplication expression tiles. Players must drag and drop the correct number bauble onto the matching tiles to solve the expressions. As each expression is solved, the winter image gradually gets revealed. The goal is to uncover the entire image by completing all the math problems correctly.', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to drag and drop the correct number bauble onto the matching tiles to solve the expressions', 'English'),
('Shoot Some Fish!', 3499, 'Become a fearless worm on a mission in Shoot Some Fish! After losing his family to hungry fish, our hero fights back! Dangling from a fishing hook, armed with a harpoon, he battles through 10 intense levels. Fish grow faster and smarter, making survival a real challenge. Use strategy and reflexes to claim victory and teach the fish a lesson they won&amp;rsquo;t forget!', 'Use Mouse Swipe to shoot Shoot fish dodge attacks and survive with 5 lives 10 challenging levels 7 unique fish with different speeds Day amp night underwater settings', 'English'),
('Parking Crazy', 3500, 'This is a casual game that combines light - hearted fun with parking challenges, allowing players to enjoy the unique pleasure of parking during their fragmented time. The game graphics adopt a fresh and cute 3D cartoon style, with bright and lively colors. The gameplay is simple and easy to pick up, yet full of depth. Players only need to click and slide the screen to control the vehicle to move forward, backward, and turn. The level design is ingenious, with the difficulty increasing gradually. In the novice levels, the venue is open and the parking spaces are spacious, helping players quickly master the operations.', 'You can control the cars forward movement reverse and steering by tapping and swiping the screen As the levels progress the difficulty of the game gradually increases Narrow spaces and multiple consecutive parking tasks will appear and players need', 'English'),
('Rush Royale Tower Defense Td', 3501, 'Rush Royale: Tower Defense TD is an exciting game that combines the fun of classic tower defense with the fun of merge mechanics. You will buy your soldiers to protect your defense towers. Such as Blade Chicken, Cannon Bear, Warrior Frag or Magic Dog.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cool Chill Guy Hidden Cheese', 3502, 'Chill Cool Hidden Cheese Guy is a delightful and relaxing hidden-object game that will test your powers of observation while immersing you in the chill world of Chill Guy. The goal is simple but highly engaging&amp;mdash;find 10 pieces of cheese cleverly hidden in each stage. With fun visuals, laid-back vibes, and a growing challenge as you progress, this game offers endless enjoyment for players of all ages. Each level features a unique picture filled with Chill Guy and his cool surroundings. At first glance, everything may seem normal, but look a little closer, and you&amp;rsquo;ll notice that pieces of cheese are hidden in plain sight. Some are tucked away i', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Color Candy Circle Hole Game', 3503, 'Colorful candies to move them into different shape holes. much entertainment game. Colorful candies to move them into different shape holes. much entertainment game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Fish Frenzy   Eat Some Fish', 3504, 'Dive into Fish Frenzy! Play as a goldfish and eat smaller fish to grow, but beware of bigger fish that can eat you! Progress through 5 unique levels and unlock 2 bonus levels. Enjoy exciting challenges with 3 different feedable fish. Can you become the biggest fish in the sea?', 'Control the goldfish with your mouse Auto-eat nearby smaller fish 5 levels 3 bonus levels Grow to take on bigger fish', 'English'),
('Fortune Wheel', 3505, 'Experience the thrill of the casino with Fortune Wheel. This game will test your luck as you spin the wheel to see what fortune has in store for you. Each successful spin can lead to a big win, turning your virtual coins into a vast fortune. However, Lady Luck is fickle and one wrong spin could cost you all your earnings or even result in bankruptcy. Hold your breath as the wheel spins and hope fate is on your side!', 'Fortune Wheel is simple yet engaging arcade game where you press the spin button to set the wheel in motion Your payoff depends on where the wheel stops If luck serves you well youll multiply your coins dramatically but land on the wrong segment and y', 'English'),
('AllPeopleTUG', 3506, 'Players are dropped onto a map and start without weapons. The map is scattered with a wealth of weapons and equipment. Players need to constantly explore and collect these resources to enhance their survival ability and combat power. The core goal of the game is to be the last survivor. Usually, there are multiple players in each game, and they are randomly distributed on the map. As the game progresses, the safe zone will gradually shrink, forcing players to gather towards the central area, increasing the chances of encounters. Players need to search for weapons and other items that can improve their survival ability.', 'Mobile Control the character to move around the map using the virtual joystick Desktop Use WSAD to move and click the icon to perform actions such as firing sprinting healing and reloading', 'English');
